data.description: Step into this impeccably remodeled 3-bedroom home! This one-level home features a spacious & open concept design w/ vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, A/C, Chef's kitchen w/granite counters, Stainless Steel appliances, breakfast bar seating & seamlessly connects to dining area & living room. Expansive great room w/French doors that lead out to an oversized 15' x 18' covered back deck, providing the perfect retreat overlooking the meticulously landscaped & fully-fenced backyard. Primary suite features walk-in closet, full bath with marble counters & slider that leads to the covered back deck. Completely remodeled from the studs out in 2015. Great location & conveniently close to shopping, parks and restaurants! Welcome home, sweet home!
